âš™ï¸ Instalasi

Clone repo:

git clone https://github.com/username/project_buku.git
cd project_buku


Install dependencies:

npm install


Konfigurasi .env:

DB_HOST=localhost
DB_USER=root
DB_PASSWORD=yourpassword
DB_NAME=perpustakaan


Jalankan server:

npm start

